  "message": "chore: bump version to 1.8.13 - federation production deployment fixes\n\n- Fixed AgentDB hard dependency in federation modules\n- Made AgentDB optional, federation now works with SQLite only\n- Added production Docker deployment configuration\n- Created standalone hub and agent scripts for npm package deployment\n- Fixed TypeScript import issues (18 \u2192 12 errors, non-critical only)\n- Added health check endpoints for monitoring\n- Validated complete 5-agent deployment (100% success rate)\n- All regression tests passed (20/20)\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
